import React from 'react'

import { Container, Row, Col } from 'reactstrap'

const Footer = () => {
    return <footer className="footer">
        <Container>
            <Row>
                <Col lg='3' md='6' sm='6'></Col>

                <Col lg='2' md='3' sm='6'></Col>
                
                <Col lg='2' md='3' sm='6'></Col>
            </Row>
        </Container>

    </footer>
}

export default Footer
